            <TITLE>
               <P>107_18 — Inspection and Maintenance of Indoor Gymnasium, Fitness and Sport Equipment and Outdoor Schools Play and Sport Equipment</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>107_18</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="50000000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>An ESPO national framework to provide reliable and competent inspection and maintenance services for traditional school (balance benches, vaulting horses etc.) and cardio vascular (treadmills, exercise bikes etc.) and strength (weight machines) gymnasium, fitness and sports equipment. Also the inspection and maintenance of schools outdoor trim trail, activity play and sport equipment and surfacing. To include repairs and any other associated services. The framework is one lot for inspection and maintenance services as the full service will be offered by one supplier for each site visit. To tender:</P>
               <P>(a) Go to www.eastmidstenders.org;</P>
               <P>(b) Register;</P>
               <P>(c) Search for tender opportunity “XXX_XX”;</P>
               <P>(d) Express an interest;</P>
               <P>(e) Download the tender from the website.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
